CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 20, 1945, pg. 1 reads: "Assigned To Motorcycle Squad - James Holt, formerly stationed in Oakland District, was transferred this week to the Motorcycle Corps by the Pittsburgh Police Department. He is the second officer to be assigned to this division. - Harris Photo.
TitMainTitle: Motorcycle patrolman James Holt, posed on police motorcycle no. 272, another version
